originalText.text:
I ordered a Mercedes Louis Hamilton hoodie from this company. I ordered a size 2XL for my son a week before Christmas. Item arrived in middle of January. The quality was very poor. It appears to be a knock-off product. Looked like someone took some thin cloth and sewed it together in a garage and ironed on some logos. The hoodie was grossly oversized, must have been a 3XL. The sleeves were 2 inches too long and the shoulders were meant for someone much bigger. There was no tag on item that showed the size.
When I emailed company and asked for refund, I was told that the order said 2XL and their shipping papers said they shipped a 2XL. So it was not their fault so no refund. Note that the item did not have a size label on it.
I suggest that you stay away from this company and only order authentic merchandise from reputable companies.
